Careers
Cloud Peak Energy offers a competitive wage and benefit package and leadership committed to developing not only the best people, but also the best in people.
Cloud Peak Energy is committed to equal employment opportunity. The company wants, and needs, to attract individuals who have the ability, skill and work ethic required at its operations. Cloud Peak Energy respects the rights of individuals to fair treatment without regard to race, color, religion, age, sex, sexual orientation, gender identity, national origin, parental status, military service or veteran status, genetic information or disability. We are an equal opportunity employer. All qualified applicants will receive consideration for employment without regard to race, color, religion, age, sex, sexual orientation, gender identity, national origin, parental status, military service or veteran status, genetic information or disability. A request for reasonable accommodation, if needed, may be oral or written and may use plain English. Requests may be given to our Human Resource department. The request may be made by an applicant, employee or by a third party, such as a relative, job coach, or friend, on his or her behalf.
Click here to view the “Equal Employment Opportunity is the Law” poster with information on rights and obligations.
