Company Profile
Sector: Energy
Industry: Oil, Gas & Coal
Sub-Industry: Coal Operations
Cloud Peak Energy Resources LLC / Cloud Peak Energy Finance Corporation is set up as a dual issuer. The Company operates as a special purpose formed in order to issue new debt securities for existing ones to satisfy general corporate purposes.




